cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.NE, cs.SI

The paper involves training and validating a multi-task LSTM on wearable heart rate sensor data to detect medical conditions. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) as well as cybernetics (cs.CY) due to the use of wearable technology. The paper also involves healthcare (cs.HC) as it deals with detecting medical conditions. Additionally, the use of semi-supervised learning methods and heuristic pretraining suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and signal processing (cs.SI).
